ly because of a lack of access to basic nutritious diets and vaccines that prevent disease.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"other children\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"their full potential\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"basic nutritious diets\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"vaccines\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"disease\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As young athletes impress and inspire global audiences, the Games are the perfect moment to reflect on how to level the playing field for all children.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"young athletes\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"global audiences\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect moment\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"the playing field\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"all children\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Integrating nutrition and immunisation as the cornerstones of healthy development can be a game-changer, ensuring every child is able to reach their full potential in whatever field they choose.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nutrition\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"immunisation\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"the cornerstones\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"healthy development\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"a game-changer\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"every child\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"their full potential\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever field\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The conditions for healthy development include both the absence of disease and presence of adequate nutrition, creating a virtuous cycle that allows children to thrive.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The conditions\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"healthy development\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"both the absence\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"disease\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"presence\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"adequate nutrition\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"a virtuous cycle\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaccines trigger the strongest immunity in children who have healthy diets, while those who are malnourished are more susceptible to infectious diseases.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vaccines\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"the strongest immunity\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"healthy diets\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"infectious diseases\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unconscionably, in this day and age, both malnutrition and preventable infectious disease claim the lives of millions of children every year.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"both malnutrition\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"preventable infectious disease\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"the lives\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Globally,more than 14 million childrenare un- or under-vaccinated - an increase of 2.7 million compared with pre-pandemic levels - while almosta quarterof children under five were stunted in 2022 as a result of inadequate diets.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an increase\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"pre-pandemic levels\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"almosta quarterof children\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"inadequate diets\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, immunisation and nutrition interventions are proven to be amongst the most cost-effective approaches to help children survive and thrive.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"immunisation and nutrition interventions\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"the most cost-effective approaches\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One dollar invested in nutrition gives a rate of return of US$16, rising to US$35 for exclusive breastfeeding, while the return on investment of immunisation in Gavi-supported countries is estimated at betweenUS$21 and US$54per US$1 spent.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One dollar\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"nutrition\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"a rate\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"return\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"exclusive breastfeeding\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"the return\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"immunisation\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"Gavi-supported countries\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1988}, {\"ngram\": \"US$54per\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is especially important for low- and middle-income countries where immunisation rates are lowest, malnutrition is prevalent and resources are stretched thin.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"low- and middle-income countries\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"immunisation rates\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"malnutrition\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"resources\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest UN figures showmore than halfof unvaccinated children live in 31 countries exposed to conflict and other vulnerabilities, disrupting access to nutrition and health services.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.8247785339856167, \"rank\": 0.21244668573240996, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"halfof unvaccinated children\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"31 countries\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"other vulnerabilities\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"nutrition and health services\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same children often miss out on both nutritional supplements and essential vaccines, meaning that integrated health services would solve two problems at once.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The same children\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"both nutritional supplements\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"essential vaccines\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"integrated health services\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"two problems\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Integrated nutrition and immunisation can be achieved either in the same clinic or community health facility, or through the same health worker.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Integrated nutrition\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"immunisation\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"the same clinic\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"community health facility\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"the same health worker\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Uganda is one country that has taken proactive action towards integration, and plans to shift to integrated provision of nutritional supplements and vaccines based on learnings from several pilot programmes.\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2703, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.928369751797281e-20, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one country\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"proactive action\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"integration\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"integrated provision\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2820}, {\"ngram\": \"nutritional supplements\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"vaccines\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"learnings\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"several pilot programmes\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Action Against Hunger and partners in Somalia mounted an integrated campaign to address rising levels of malnutrition and disease during the prolonged drought in 2022, which affected 7.8 million people.\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2961, \"end\": 2968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somalia\", \"score\": 0.9999999996880433, \"rank\": 3.1206091078635033e-10, \"text\": \"Somalia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somalia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Somalia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Action\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"Hunger\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2944}, {\"ngram\": \"partners\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"an integrated campaign\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"rising levels\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"malnutrition\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"disease\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3052}, {\"ngram\": \"the prolonged drought\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"7.8 million people\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The campaign reached more than 200,000 children with measles vaccines, deworming treatments and vitamin A supplementation, and screened more than 185,000 children under five for wasting.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The campaign\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200,000 children\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"measles vaccines\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"treatments\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"vitamin\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"A supplementation\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 185,000 children\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the referral sites for severe acute malnutrition, the average cure rate was 83 per cent and malnutrition decreased significantly over the period of the campaign.\", \"from\": 3314, 